flowchart TD
    Start([User requests<br/>matched jobs]) --> FetchProfile[Fetch UserProfile<br/>Skills · Seniority · Salary<br/>Location · JobType]

    FetchProfile --> FetchJobs[Fetch Active Jobs<br/>from Database]

    FetchJobs --> Loop{For each job}

    Loop -->|next job| TechScore[Technology Score — 40%]
    TechScore --> TechCalc{Compute Jaccard<br/>Similarity}
    TechCalc -->|intersection / union| TechReason[Generate reason<br/>Matched: React, .NET<br/>Missing: Kubernetes]

    TechReason --> SeniorityScore[Seniority Score — 20%]
    SeniorityScore --> SeniorityCalc{Map levels to integers<br/>Junior=0 … Director=5<br/>Compute proximity}
    SeniorityCalc --> SeniorityReason[Generate reason<br/>Senior vs Mid — close match]

    SeniorityReason --> SalaryScore[Salary Score — 15%]
    SalaryScore --> SalaryCalc{Compute range<br/>overlap}
    SalaryCalc -->|intersection / max range| SalaryReason[Generate reason<br/>Ranges overlap<br/>60k–80k]

    SalaryReason --> LocationScore[Location Score — 15%]
    LocationScore --> LocationCheck{Is Remote?}
    LocationCheck -->|Yes + user open| LocFull[Score = 1.0]
    LocationCheck -->|No| CityMatch{City / State /<br/>Country match?}
    CityMatch -->|exact city| LocHigh[Score = 0.9]
    CityMatch -->|same country| LocMed[Score = 0.5]
    CityMatch -->|no match| LocLow[Score = 0.1]
    LocFull & LocHigh & LocMed & LocLow --> LocReason[Generate reason]

    LocReason --> JobTypeScore[Job Type Score — 10%]
    JobTypeScore --> JobTypeCalc{Exact match?}
    JobTypeCalc -->|Yes| JTFull[Score = 1.0]
    JobTypeCalc -->|Partial| JTMed[Score = 0.5]
    JobTypeCalc -->|No| JTLow[Score = 0.0]
    JTFull & JTMed & JTLow --> JTReason[Generate reason]

    JTReason --> TotalCalc[Total Score =<br/>Tech×0.4 + Seniority×0.2 +<br/>Salary×0.15 + Location×0.15 +<br/>JobType×0.1]

    TotalCalc --> StoreResult[Store MatchedJobDto<br/>with breakdown]
    StoreResult --> Loop

    Loop -->|all done| Sort[Sort by TotalScore<br/>descending]
    Sort --> Filter{Filter above<br/>threshold?}
    Filter -->|Yes| Return[Return top matches<br/>with breakdown]
    Filter -->|GetTopMatches| TopN[Return top N results]
    Return & TopN --> End([Response to client])
